      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would serve well as a dependable daily driver or a secondary work car. While it remains mechanically sound, the exterior shows clear signs of age, including several noticeable scratches and some fading in the clear coat on the roof. Inside, the upholstery has some visible staining and wear on the driver's seat bolster. It has been serviced regularly, but it is due for a new set of tires soon and could benefit from some cosmetic detailing.",
