      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to a standard that transcends the typical secondary market offering. This unit displays an impeccable aesthetic profile, characterized by a flawless exterior and a cabin that remains in showroom state. Every aspect of this vehicle has been curated to ensure an unrivaled driving experience, representing a premier acquisition for the most demanding enthusiast. This is an invitation to secure a specimen of rare mechanical and cosmetic integrity.",
